moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得d窮撚先會話上海好住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係香港,你有錢,真係乜都得<br />\n衣食住行根本好方便"},{"pid":"8fd364444383f92ab7ff0430ae964c2d8c38b7dc","tid":292452,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"早十幾年前<br />\n連上海妹都可以係深圳包到<br />\n而家難左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我老母話我知"},{"pid":"099777a0351b1e2782169920d69058d92b6a0b26","tid":292452,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"上海 食野平既10蚊一餐 貴既香港一樣<br />\n係空氣差但夏天都唔熱"},{"pid":"2be536c25f66ddebf8f59f0f18638b5a4ee3e058","tid":292452,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"有錢嘅話香港真係天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d10600c438e207852c206dcda5075a19aeeec1","tid":292452,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早十幾年前<br />\n連上海妹都可以係深圳包到<br />\n而家難左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我老母話我知</blockquote><br />\n上海妹既樣最多排10名內，最正係黑龍江,重慶,四川呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意食辣既香港人去四川呢D住一定爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我指菊花......"},{"pid":"20fc6442950cb75b49943db0a7b98883be603ab6","tid":292452,"uid":62391,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e86f6c9170c31057ff0e12ddffd4f00aa954cdb","tid":292452,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44ba6a775b01047cf14c8972c247b6c70a785e10","tid":292452,"uid":3117,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"呢個post 都幾多大陸仔/五毛"},{"pid":"0b6a1274388aab7227b990f1f54e241a0ca21360","tid":292452,"uid":57705,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79ec1bde78026c9f1eab7ace126785fcb8806827","tid":292452,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早十幾年前<br />\n連上海妹都可以係深圳包到<br />\n而家難左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 我老母話我知</blockquote><br />\n上海妹既樣最多排10名內，最正係黑龍江,重慶,四川呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意食辣既香港人去四川呢D住一定爽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我指菊花......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遲d 有埋高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建設淫賤中國"},{"pid":"7461d74900b6db7a53d4e5611ce02b914e8a6f61","tid":292452,"uid":75100,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上海 食野平既10蚊一餐 貴既香港一樣<br />\n係空氣差但夏天都唔熱</blockquote><br />\n冬天好凍（對香港人黎講）</blockquote><br />\n所以上海真係要諗下....空氣天氣都麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 北京就空氣差，但天氣就完美，春夏秋冬會感受到，唔似香港變得咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係杭州既話，就根本唔使諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅正既城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb470ce688f2ea04ef0e2fad2448284446c8229","tid":292452,"uid":12661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上海 食野平既10蚊一餐 貴既香港一樣<br />\n係空氣差但夏天都唔熱</blockquote><br />\n10蚊一餐嗰啲唔知巴打敢唔敢食&hellip;<br />\n就算巴打夠膽，我都係勸你唔好試&hellip;"},{"pid":"b0471d00c1355c8aedbf61b356841c440efaeecf","tid":292452,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"460f