>\n啲撚樣都係會周圍痾尿 出入靠渣車 坐巴士地鐵坐撚到你傻 坐飛機去邊都例牌delay 玩女貴(有平既但果啲樣狗都不屌) 諗到再後補<br />\n<br />\n香港生活節奏急促好多 夏天熱到仆街 冬天都係熱到仆街 搵幾多洗幾多<br />\n但我上海搵12000 個個月都有幾千剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a131ae336d6e25605eecca8f932bcfe0c84c7c6","tid":292452,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"係啦 上海好好<br />\n一早超越香港啦講幾百年<br />\n快撚d去支那嘆世界啦"},{"pid":"641f8446ccc7976d2a46ab2c257157e0f083fa05","tid":292452,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上海 食野平既10蚊一餐 貴既香港一樣<br />\n係空氣差但夏天都唔熱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食好野肯定貴過香港<br />\n進口都打稅<br />\n和牛 南非鮑 貴到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324a4e1715b6b5a906c4fe2979f58a7988d4c84d","tid":292452,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"竟然有人係到吹捧 大陸城市, 真係笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你想住住下, 突然比人拆樓<br />\n定係想日日食 地溝油, 吸毒霧??<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f963dcaca91361da4e812fd71f2f9bd876e6a871","tid":292452,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4868949c57f41eee2f7db76a1efa99f79059444","tid":292452,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ef9286b1c10431b7b051195a79f3f3eaee5a319","tid":292452,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"上海好住, 快啲走"},{"pid":"92461c4d01e7425b51697502aaed1190b5583d16","tid":292452,"uid":78273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有屋有車 唔憂生活 我揀香港</blockquote><br />\n正想講<br />\n又有屋又有車仲要唔憂生活<br />\n香港根本好住到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces