/>\n<br />\n反而當地後生仔好有禮貌，<br />\n傾過幾句，佢地都好憎D外省人但係又無撚計，<br />\n凳佢地慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8813df93944cde52f1ce0d07d8fa9df353936f94","tid":292452,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔講上海嘅生活指數同香港係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去上海不如去其他二線城市算啦"},{"pid":"7d16b5f0a4f6017c93e479950c46cbc5be8d167f","tid":292452,"uid":90791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"上海妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa98a765e31bd92f22f9589b8fa3b546ae0b306a","tid":292452,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6a37362f0bf5453cc984631c6a98ec060fd5874","tid":292452,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"樓上話10蚊平你又屌<br />\n咁你咪試下食囉<br />\n<br />\n我就唔得喇<br />\n一家人去食宵夜<br />\n番黎一齊嘔到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f6587e7677f6d061bd52f41be4c8d98e455d4e","tid":292452,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有屋有車 唔憂生活 我揀香港</blockquote><br />\n正想講<br />\n又有屋又有車仲要唔憂生活<br />\n香港根本好住到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger <br />\n香港只要有錢所有問題已解決</blockquote><br />\n有錢既話<br />\n邊到都好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d